  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nIf a block with a lower slot is selected as a higher scoring one, we need to reorg the chain to match this result. This would entail adding reorg logic within the `updateHead` function after merging #643, leveraging persisted states for unfinalized blocks, and building up a new chain from the last finalized slot upwards.\r\n\r\nA PR for this would also include pretty exhaustive tests for various reorg scenarios.",
